                          <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3985Mazmura">መዝሙረ፡ ድንግል፡</title>
                          <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                          <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                          ነዓ፡ ኀቤየ፡ ንጉሠ፡ እስራኤል፡ <lb/>
                        በዓለ፡ መዝሙር፡ ሠናይ፡ ወጥዑመ፡ ቃል፡ <lb/>
