                        እንዘ፡ እጸርኅ፡ ወእብል፡ <lb/>
                      </incipit>
                          <note>The text is accompanied by the <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur">Mazmura Dāwit</ref>.
                          </note>
                        </msItem>
